'''生物多样性和生态系统服务政府间科学政策平台'''（{{lang-en|'''I'''ntergovernmental science-policy '''P'''latform on '''B'''iodiversity and '''E'''cosystem '''S'''ervices}}，缩写：'''IPBES'''）是[[联合国环境规划署|联合国环境规划署]]整合[[千年生态系统评估|千年生态系统评估]]的后续行动和[[生物多样性科学知识国际机制|生物多样性科学知识国际机制]]所形成的一个框架。2012年4月在[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]正式成立，秘书处设在德国[[波恩|波恩]]。功能類似於聯合國[[政府間氣候變化專門委員會|政府間氣候變化專門委員會]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2012/01/120120010357.htm|title=Biodiversity crisis is worse than climate change, experts say|date=2012-01-20|website={{tsl|en|ScienceDaily|每日科學|ScienceDaily}}|access-date=2019-09-11|archive-date=2021-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211229035952/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2012/01/120120010357.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

IPBES旨在应对[[生物多样性|生物多样性]]丧失和[[生態系服務|生態系服務]]功能退化问题，在[[科学|科学]]与[[政策|政策]]之间建立联系，以期加强生物多样性的保护与可持续利用，确保长期人类福祉和[[可持续发展|可持续发展]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ipbes.net |title=IPBES |author=<!--Not stated--> |access-date=2019-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190627065419/https://www.ipbes.net/ |archive-date=2019-06-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 建立和早期發展 ==
2010年，{{tsl|en|Sixty-fifth session of the United Nations General Assembly|第65屆聯合國大會|第65屆}}[[聯合國大會|聯合國大會]]的一項決議敦促[[聯合國環境規劃署|聯合國環境規劃署]]召開全體會議以建立IPBES。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Vadrot|first=Alice B. M.|last2=Rankovic|first2=Aleksandar|last3=Lapeyre|first3=Renaud|last4=Aubert|first4=Pierre-Marie|last5=Laurans|first5=Yann|date=2018-03-01|title=Why are social sciences and humanities needed in the works of IPBES? A systematic review of the literature|journal=Innovation: The European Journal of Social Science Research |volume=31|issue="Suppl 1"|pages=78–100|doi=10.1080/13511610.2018.1443799|issn=1351-1610|pmc=5898424|pmid=29706803}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Duraiappah|first=Anantha Kumar|last2=Rogers|first2=Deborah|date=September 2011|title=The Intergovernmental Platform on Biodiversity and Ecosystem Services: opportunities for the social sciences|journal=Innovation: The European Journal of Social Science Research|language=en|volume=24|issue=3|pages=217–224|doi=10.1080/13511610.2011.592052|issn=1351-1610}}</ref>2013年，全體會議為未來IPBES通過初步的概念框架。<ref name=":0" />

2019年4月29日至5月4日，132個IPBES成員國代表於法國[[巴黎|巴黎]]召開會議，聆聽IPBES的《{{tsl|en|Global Assessment Report on Biodiversity and Ecosystem Services|全球生物多樣性與生態系服務評估報告}}》全文<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ipbes.net/global-assessment |title=Global Assessment Report on Biodiversity and Ecosystem Services |date=2019 |publisher=IPBES |access-date=2020-12-06 |archive-date=2022-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112000727/https://ipbes.net/global-assessment |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並通過報告摘要供相關決策者參考。2019年5月6日，該份40頁的摘要被發布。<ref name="IPBES">{{cite web|title=Media Release: Nature's Dangerous Decline 'Unprecedented'; Species Extinction Rates 'Accelerating'|website=IPBES|url=https://www.ipbes.net/news/Media-Release-Global-Assessment|access-date=2019-05-06|archive-date=2019-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614220133/https://www.ipbes.net/news/Media-Release-Global-Assessment|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ru.nl/english/news-agenda/news/vm/management/2019/nature-decline-unprecedented-human-history-1/|title=Nature's decline 'unprecedented' in human history: 1 million species threatened with extinction|website=Radboud University|access-date=2021-07-05|archive-date=2021-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712071159/https://www.ru.nl/english/news-agenda/news/vm/management/2019/nature-decline-unprecedented-human-history-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

